{"title":"End to End book extract (plus podcast with the author, Paul Jones)","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/end-to-end-book-extract/","date":1617357644000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=90&#038;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1440,959 1440w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/end-to-end-book-paul-jones-1240763.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w, \" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-624271 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"End to End by Paul Jones, ISBN 1408712733\" title=\"End to End by Paul Jones, ISBN 1408712733\" />                                            <p><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/accessories/books/end-to-end-book-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">End to End</span></i></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> by Paul Jones is a wonderful, well-researched and very funny book about the Land’s End to John O’Groats cycling record, as well as Jones’s own journey along the route. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Regulated by the <a href=\"http://www.rra.org.uk/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Road Records Association</a> since 1881, the ~841-mile ride demands riders go to extremes of training, preparation and endurance in the pursuit of – paraphrasing Jones’s words – beating the measure by which all other cycling achievements in the UK are compared. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The book explores both the men’s and women’s records (as well as the decidedly odd and anachronistic trike records).</span></p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--aspect\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% / 1.501210653753);\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=169%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=338%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=507%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=677%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=169%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=338%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=507%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-74398994-7bd5da0.jpg?